44a5f959d003fafa642dbe9c","tid":2039001,"uid":213028,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T15:25:19.000Z","msg":"首選葡萄牙<br />\n<br />\n非常好"},{"pid":"cece35a29c0ceebe3c1cd35124ef7008bb931279","tid":2039001,"uid":80535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T18:47:37.000Z","msg":"睇下你要咩<br />\n海既話基本上呢幾個國家全部都有<br />\n<br />\n想平消費Hea下睇下既咪葡萄牙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />波圖可以考慮吓<br />\n西班牙就人文風情多，不過好睇邊個城市，巴塞同西維爾華倫西亞或者巴斯克地區可以差好遠，同埋去西班牙既去內陸城市睇古蹟同建築好過啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n南法夠嘆，行下市集海邊又一日，尼斯同馬賽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n意大利同南法一樣消費貴，而且南意北意風氣文化差好遠，北意可以考慮熱拿亞或者佛羅蘭斯，睇古蹟/城市景色，又近海<br />\n但如果去意大利建議你兩日一個城市，因為其實一個城市唔算多野玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />如果未去過歐洲就唔建議你去拿玻里果啲南意城市，治安差到一個極點<br />\n克羅地亞消費平，自由海景應該係呢幾個入面最好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但留意返南歐治安普遍較差，好多吉卜賽人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />摩納哥、巴塞、米蘭、同埋普通南法既小城市會相對好少少，南意、西西里同普遍西班牙既城市都唔撚掂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c345cb0b4d658f5bd71f37daba35bcee6101919","tid":2039001,"uid":118346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T03:20:38.000Z","msg":"葡萄牙乳豬飯 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}